Written by Marshall Wilson 
Started: 1/27/2021
Updated: 1/27/2021

This project is intended to be a webapp that will use data from a user's 
spotify profile (top genres, followed playlists, listening patterns, etc.) 
and a k-means clustering model based on previous users to predict the 
astrological sign of the user. 

* Recognition * 
    Thanks to Traversy Media, whose python webapp tutorial was helpful in the 
        development of the initial prototype 
    Thanks to the-pudding whose "bad music analyzer" inspired this project 